Required parameters : None

None

Encoding considerations : binary
This media type may require encoding on transports not capable of handling binary.

Security considerations :
This MIME type represents game data files, such as protected levels or tracks.
Where necessary, the content of these files will be protected using OMA DRM 2.
OMA DRM 2 is not specific to the type. It is an industry standard
external service used to encrypt and decrypt data.

The type does not contain any executable content.

None
